# Shows Data

## Source
- Default: local `shows.csv` (headers: `Title,Date,Location,Link`)
- Production option: set `SHOWS_CSV_URL` in `app.js` to a published Google Sheets CSV
- Maintainer guide: `HOW-TO-UPDATE-SHOWS.txt` (not linked on the public site)

## Parsing rules
- Simple comma-split — avoid commas inside Location names
- Empty `Link` → no Buy Tickets button
- Filter out shows with `Date` before today
- Sort remaining shows by date ascending
- Escape HTML when rendering CSV fields into the DOM

## Public UI
- Section `#shows` — user-facing copy only ("Coming Up"), no file paths
